Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的以为靠一次军事介入就能结束持续了300多年的纷争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只一次  会一直介入的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至纷争结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至憎恨指向我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是伴随改变事物的疼痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会被干掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是首次介入纷争  他有自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他会是Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合的运输机？  在这个空域？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Flag吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:21:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:21:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉哈姆·艾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你的存在夺走了内心的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能接受连对话都要拒绝的行为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对摆在眼前的刀刃  少年感受到了时代的变革
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「变化的世界」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是无法指定的现实


